[l] Haha, grossartig: Und noch ein Mitglied der griechischen Verhandlungs-Delegation packt aus, und zwar pikanterweise in einer franzoesischen Zeitung. Und was sagt er so?The advisor cites threats proffered to Varoufakis by Eurogroup president Jeroen Dijsselbloem, warning he would sink Greece's banks unless the Tsipras government bowed to the harsh deal on offer, and by German finance minister Wolfgang Schaeuble, who he says demanded: "How much money do you want to leave the euro?"Wie geil! (Danke, Patrick)
